{"title":"10个产品设计Claude Skills","slug":"txw4z525f02mmw64","summary":"Anthropic 的 AI 助手 Claude 已经成为产品设计师工具箱中最全能的工具之一，其能力远不止于生成代码。 从快速原型设计与设计评审，到用户研究汇总与无障碍设计审计，Claude 几乎可以应用于设计流程的每个阶段。关键在于知道在 何时 触发 Claude 的 哪些 能","category":"AI设计Skill","tags":["PART1️⃣ AI设计工作流&Vibe Coding","Claude Code + Figma","AI设计Skill"],"featured":false,"order":18,"level":3,"updatedAt":"2026-04-19","wordCount":3151,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/txw4z525f02mmw64","html":"<h3 data-lake-id=\"VnqfQ\" id=\"VnqfQ\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub9f4a096\" id=\"ub9f4a096\">Anthropic 的 AI 助手 Claude 已经成为产品设计师工具箱中最全能的工具之一，其能力远不止于生成代码。</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"udeebccc1\" id=\"udeebccc1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ued005b3d\" id=\"ued005b3d\">从快速原型设计与设计评审，到用户研究汇总与无障碍设计审计，Claude 几乎可以应用于设计流程的每个阶段。关键在于知道在</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6598e142\" id=\"u6598e142\">何时</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8eb8be77\" id=\"u8eb8be77\">触发 Claude 的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue33ec783\" id=\"ue33ec783\">哪些</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b528e25\" id=\"u5b528e25\">能力。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucf49dbf8\" id=\"ucf49dbf8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u819b4d41\" id=\"u819b4d41\">在本文中，我将分享我最喜欢的 10 个 Claude 技能（Skills），它们帮助我极大地简化了产品设计工作流。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"RA4cc\" id=\"RA4cc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1dec0c22\" id=\"u1dec0c22\">如何在 Claude 中导入 skill?</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ue16d76f8\" id=\"ue16d76f8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u90b735a5\" id=\"u90b735a5\">我将对本文列出的所有技能使用一种常规格式。每个技能都是一个 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua5196bf8\" id=\"ua5196bf8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u91a8f0ed\" id=\"u91a8f0ed\">skill.md</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf94c6af2\" id=\"uf94c6af2\"> 文件（.md 代表 markdown 格式），包含以下几个部分：</span></p><ul list=\"ufd68ae3f\"><li fid=\"u5eec42a0\" data-lake-id=\"uda19d785\" id=\"uda19d785\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u06460e5e\" id=\"u06460e5e\">YAML front matter（前置元数据）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6f78a85f\" id=\"u6f78a85f\"> → 定义技能的元数据（名称、描述、路由信号），以便 Claude 知道</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubaa9a275\" id=\"ubaa9a275\">何时</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u545524d4\" id=\"u545524d4\">以及</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4edf6df8\" id=\"u4edf6df8\">为何</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua5ca1356\" id=\"ua5ca1356\">使用它。你将使用“name（名称）”在 Claude 中调用该技能。</span></li><li fid=\"u5eec42a0\" data-lake-id=\"uaa1915c1\" id=\"uaa1915c1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5035eaab\" id=\"u5035eaab\">Role（角色）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufe1418c1\" id=\"ufe1418c1\"> → Claude 在执行该技能时应采用的专业知识与视角。</span></li><li fid=\"u5eec42a0\" data-lake-id=\"ud9c4fdc0\" id=\"ud9c4fdc0\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4923e96b\" id=\"u4923e96b\">Task（任务）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4c15782e\" id=\"u4c15782e\"> → 该技能应产出的单一且明确的结果。</span></li><li fid=\"u5eec42a0\" data-lake-id=\"u9bd23284\" id=\"u9bd23284\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub68782d1\" id=\"ub68782d1\">Input（输入）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u28582475\" id=\"u28582475\"> → 指定用户必须提供的背景信息与产出物，以确保准确执行。</span></li><li fid=\"u5eec42a0\" data-lake-id=\"u354e0e72\" id=\"u354e0e72\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u67b2f13d\" id=\"u67b2f13d\">Workflow（工作流）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubf527b3c\" id=\"ubf527b3c\"> → 将推理过程分解为多个步骤，以产出高质量结果。</span></li><li fid=\"u5eec42a0\" data-lake-id=\"uca7ee857\" id=\"uca7ee857\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4546b082\" id=\"u4546b082\">Output format（输出格式）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub2c2c5d6\" id=\"ub2c2c5d6\"> → 要求 Claude 以可在文档中复用的结构生成输出。</span></li><li fid=\"u5eec42a0\" data-lake-id=\"u5be0c961\" id=\"u5be0c961\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udbda30c1\" id=\"udbda30c1\">Quality bar（质量标准）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue9c246dc\" id=\"ue9c246dc\"> → 定义 Claude 产出结果的成功标准。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u16f1aeb1\" id=\"u16f1aeb1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u57a36567\" id=\"u57a36567\">你可以通过多种方式将技能导入到你的 Claude 中。最简单的方法是在 Claude 网页版中进行。跳转到 Settings（设置）→ Capabilities（功能）→ Skills（技能），点击“Add（添加）”并以上传 .md 文件的形式上传技能。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucb2cc083\" id=\"ucb2cc083\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1774187310358-9f87c472-7285-4b82-bcdc-da598a0ace4a.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud8f19efa-7968-4958-a5ce-e8595d31023%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ub5d5a001-71a0-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A700%2C%22height%22%3A396%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A215155%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A791%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22MEMORY%20CLAUDE%20GENERAL%20SEARCH%20AND%20REFERENCE%20CHATS%20NEW%20CHAT%20ALLOW%20CLAUDE%20TO%20SEARCH%20FOR%20RELEVANT%20DETAILS%20IN%20PAST%20CHATS.L%20ACCOUNT%20SEARCH%20PRIVACY%20GENERATE%20MEMORY%20FROM%20CHAT%20HISTORY%20ALLOW%20CLAUDE%20TO%20REMEMBER%20RELEVANT%20CONTEXT%20FROM%20YOUR%20CHA%20BILLING%20CHATS%20CLAUDE.LEARN%20MORE.%20PROJECTS%20USAGE%20ARTIFACTS%20CAPABILITIES%20NEW%20SKILL%20CODE%20CONNECTORS%20RECENTS%20CREATE%20WITH%20CLAUDE%20CLAUDE%20CODE%20BUILD%20COMPLEX%20SKILLS%20THROUGH%20CONVERSATION%20WRITE%20SKILL%20INSTRUCTIONS%20GREAT%20FOR%20SKILLS%20THAT%20ARE%20EASY%20TO%20DESCRIBE%20UPLOAD%20A%20SKILL%20IMPORTAZIP.SKILL%2CORMDFILE%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A838%2C%22y%22%3A-2%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22MEMORY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A22%2C%22y%22%3A20%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22CLAUDE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A469%2C%22y%22%3A37%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22GENERAL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A839%2C%22y%22%3A59%2C%22width%22%3A270%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22SEARCH%20AND%20REFERENCE%20CHATS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A63%2C%22y%22%3A94%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22NEW%20CHAT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A840%2C%22y%22%3A95%2C%22width%22%3A553%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22ALLOW%20CLAUDE%20TO%20SEARCH%20FOR%20RELEVANT%20DETAILS%20IN%20PAST%20CHATS.L%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A469%2C%22y%22%3A98%2C%22width%22%3A85%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22ACCOUNT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A63%2C%22y%22%3A143%2C%22width%22%3A70%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22SEARCH%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A467%2C%22y%22%3A155%2C%22width%22%3A76%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22PRIVACY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A839%2C%22y%22%3A161%2C%22width%22%3A352%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22GENERATE%20MEMORY%20FROM%20CHAT%20HISTORY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A837%2C%22y%22%3A198%2C%22width%22%3A562%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22ALLOW%20CLAUDE%20TO%20REMEMBER%20RELEVANT%20CONTEXT%20FROM%20YOUR%20CHA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A468%2C%22y%22%3A213%2C%22width%22%3A66%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22BILLING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A65%2C%22y%22%3A215%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22CHATS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A841%2C%22y%22%3A227%2C%22width%22%3A192%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22CLAUDE.LEARN%20MORE.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A64%2C%22y%22%3A265%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22PROJECTS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A468%2C%22y%22%3A273%2C%22width%22%3A65%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22USAGE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A64%2C%22y%22%3A311%2C%22width%22%3A88%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22ARTIFACTS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A469%2C%22y%22%3A332%2C%22width%22%3A119%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22CAPABILITIES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A752%2C%22y%22%3A348%2C%22width%22%3A114%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22NEW%20SKILL%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A64%2C%22y%22%3A362%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22CODE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A469%2C%22y%22%3A391%2C%22width%22%3A118%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22CONNECTORS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A21%2C%22y%22%3A427%2C%22width%22%3A73%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22RECENTS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A835%2C%22y%22%3A433%2C%22width%22%3A193%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22CREATE%20WITH