ng工作，并为你提供结构化的研究输出，你可以将其直接输入到你最喜欢的用户研究工具（如 NotebookLM）中。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22plain%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22---%5Cnname%3A%20user-interview-synthesizer%5Cndescription%3A%20%E5%B0%86%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%AE%BF%E8%B0%88%E8%BD%AC%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%BA%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E6%B4%9E%E5%AF%9F%E3%80%81JTBD%EF%BC%88%E5%BE%85%E5%8A%9E%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E7%97%9B%E7%82%B9%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%BA%E4%BC%9A%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%5Cn---%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%5Cn%E4%BD%A0%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E8%B5%84%E6%B7%B1%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%91%98%20(Senior%20UX%20Researcher)%E3%80%82%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%5Cn%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E8%AE%BF%E8%B0%88%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%B9%B6%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%8F%AF%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E6%B4%9E%E5%AF%9F%E3%80%82%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%5Cn-%20%E8%AE%BF%E8%B0%88%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E6%88%96%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%5Cn-%20%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%5Cn-%20%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%B5%81%5Cn1.%20%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8C%96%E5%8E%9F%E5%A7%8B%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%5Cn2.%20%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%20%20%20-%20%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%20(Goals)%5Cn%20%20%20-%20%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA%20(Behaviours)%5Cn%20%20%20-%20%E7%97%9B%E7%82%B9%20(Pain%20points)%5Cn%20%20%20-%20%E5%8F%98%E9%80%9A%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%2F%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%20(Workarounds)%5Cn3.%20%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%81%9A%E7%B1%BB%20(Cluster%20themes)%5Cn4.%20%E6%98%A0%E5%B0%84%E5%88%B0%20JTBD%EF%BC%88%E5%BE%85%E5%8A%9E%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%89%5Cn5.%20%E6%8F%90%E7%82%BC%E6%9C%BA%E4%BC%9A%E7%82%B9%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%5Cn-%20%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81%5Cn-%20%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%5Cn-%20JTBD%5Cn-%20%E7%97%9B%E7%82%B